%h2 Tags
- if tags.present?
  %table.table
    - %w[rank name items].each do |sort_option|
      %th= sortable_link(sort_option, sort, order, 'scoreboard_hub_path')

    - tags.each do |tag|
      %tr
        %td
          = tag[:rank]
        %td
          = tag[:name]
        %td
          = tag[:count]
  = render partial: 'shared/paginate', locals: { param_name: 'tags_page', anchor: 'tags-scoreboard' }, object: tags, as: :results
- else
  This hub currently has no tags scoreboard.
